            <h2>Synovitis Treatment</h2>
            <p>Synovitis is when the synovium of a joint becomes inflamed. synovial is the connective tissue that lines the inside of the joint capsule. A joint capsule is a bubble-like structure that surrounds joints such as the shoulder, elbow, knee, and ankle. It is composed of a tough, and a soft inside layer Contained inside both layers is synovial fluid, a viscous liquid that lubricates the joint to reduce friction on the articular cartilage during motion.</p>
